name: Naka Go
description: Naka Go ($NAKA) is a cultural tribute token on the Ethereum blockchain honoring Naka Go of Akaishi-so, the foundational Shiba Inu who played a pivotal role in preserving and reviving the breed after World War II. The project celebrates Shiba Inu heritage through community engagement, historical storytelling, and digital collectibles. $NAKA aims to connect dog lovers, breed historians, and crypto enthusiasts by offering a unique blend of education, community participation, and decentralized ownership.
